<li id="cite_note-Metcalfe1993-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Metcalfe1993_8-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Metcalfe1993_8-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Metcalfe1993_8-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Metcalfe1993_8-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Metcalfe1993_8-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Metcalfe1993_8-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Metcalfe1993_8-6"><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Metcalfe1993_8-7"><sup><i><b>h</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Metcalfe1993_8-8"><sup><i><b>i</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Metcalfe1993_8-9"><sup><i><b>j</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFVogel1993" class="citation book cs1">Vogel, Dan (1993). "2". In Metcalfe, Brent (ed.). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/NewApproachesToTheBookOfMormon/page/n39/mode/2up"><i>New Approaches to the Book of Mormon:Explorations in Critical Methodology</i></a>. Signature Books. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-56085-017-5" title="Special:BookSources/1-56085-017-5"><bdi>1-56085-017-5</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=2&amp;rft.btitle=New+Approaches+to+the+Book+of+Mormon%3AExplorations+in+Critical+Methodology&amp;rft.pub=Signature+Books&amp;rft.date=1993&amp;rft.isbn=1-56085-017-5&amp;rft.aulast=Vogel&amp;rft.aufirst=Dan&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2FNewApproachesToTheBookOfMormon%2Fpage%2Fn39%2Fmode%2F2up&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AUniversalism+and+the+Latter+Day+Saint+movement" class="Z3988"></span></span>
