<li id="cite_note-Ford2005-22"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Ford2005_22-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Ford, C. D. (2005). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.dialoguejournal.com/articles/lehi-on-the-great-issues-book-of-mormon-theology-in-early-nineteenth-century-perspective/">Lehi on the Great Issues: Book of Mormon Theology in Early Nineteenth-Century Perspective.</a> Dialogue Journal, 38(4), 75–96.</span>
